<TEXT>
two pilots who blew the whistle on 
safety violations at the rock island arsenal say theyve been 
grounded discredited and assigned to minor jobs in reprisal 
the army credits the two civilian pilots curt mcrae 40 and 
lloyd williams 50 with providing evidence that led to improvements 
in safety but arsenal officials deny any action has been taken to 
punish the pilots 
mcraes supervisors said he was grounded because of mental 
instability a claim mcrae denies 
i spent 13 months in vietnam with the marines that was a 
