movement crushed by the military june 34 was ousted from all his 
posts on june 24 and replaced by jiang 
jiang 62 by assuming leadership of the 47millionmember 
communist party became the post powerful political figure in china 
besides deng who retains the last word in all major decisions 
although he has resigned from all but one of his official posts 
deng is still chairman of the central military commission a 
crucial post in a nation where the military has a major say in 
politics particularly after the military suppression of student 
