here are brief sketches of key figures in 
jordans royal family 
king hussein the grandson of jordans founder king abdullah 
the 53yearold monarch has ruled for 36 of jordans 41 years of 
independence his family draws its legitimacy from its history as 
guardians of mecca islams holiest city and its descent from the 
prophet mohammed 
queen noor the americanborn daughter of former pan am airlines 
chairman najeeb halaby an arabamerican she met hussein while 
doing contract work for royal jordanian airways and married him in 
1979 husseins fourth wife she has given him four children prince 
hamzeh 9 prince hashim 8 princess iman 6 and princess raiyah 
3 the princetoneducated queen 38 sponsors womens societies 
social work and arts she also acts as a goodwill ambassador 
crown prince hassan the younger of husseins two brothers 
hassan 42 was named crown prince in 1965 while earning a degree in 
oriental studies at oxford in england noted as the palace 
intellectual he oversees economic development and sponsors seminars 
on a wide range of topics he is married to the pakistaniborn 
princess tharwat they have four children although the royal line 
is due to return to husseins offspring 
queen zein the queen mother she was the wife of the late king 
talal husseins father who abdicated due to mental illness in 
1952 she was an important adviser in the early days of husseins 
reign but now in her 70s plays a lowkey role 
prince ali husseins eldest child by an arab mother the late 
queen alia ali 13 is designated to become king after hassan the 
remainder of the line of succession is open to constitutional 
interpretation of the question of the children having nonarab 
mothers the americanborn queen noor and the britishborn princess 
muna husseins previous wife 
prince abdullah husseins eldest child he was named crown 
prince at birth in 1962 but the title was later given to hassan due 
to political turmoil at the time and because abdullahs mother 
britishborn princess muna husseins second wife was not arab the 
prince 27 has inherited husseins interest in rallycar racing and 
flying he attended prep schools in the united states studied at 
britains sandhurst military academy and is an army lieutenant he 
sometimes acts as regent when both hussein and hassan are abroad 
prince faisal husseins second son by muna faisal 25 is an 
air force pilot who won honors at a military training course in 
britain he studied electrical engineering at brown university in 
providence ri and has played an increasingly visible role 
sometimes acting as regent 
</TEXT>
